rows.label: bf03180100_0020
rows.name:
Hey, hold still. You're a boy so
you should be able to endure this much.

rows.label: bf03180100_0030
rows.name: Gimme a break. Pain is pain, isn't it?

rows.label: bf03180100_0070
rows.name:
You did that on purpose just now, didn't you?
You did it on purpose, right? Right?

rows.label: bf03180100_0080
rows.name:
I didn't, I didn't!
I just applied it normally...

rows.label: bf03180100_0090
rows.name:
Rex! You rubbed it too hard!
It hurts, see!

rows.label: bf03180100_0160
rows.name: What in the world happened here?

rows.label: bf03180100_0170
rows.name: Why do you, a Blade, still have wounds?

rows.label: bf03180100_0180
rows.name: And they're exactly the same as Rex's!
